      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to drive. It's in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and is ready for its next adventure with you! It\u2019s been well-loved and is perfect for anyone wanting a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it!",
