    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused example featuring a robust 3.0L twin-scroll turbocharged inline-six, delivering linear power through a crisp 8-speed ZF automatic transmission. This chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, complemented by an active M-Sport rear differential for precise torque vectoring. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring neutral handling characteristics under lateral load. Recent service includes a walnut blasting of the intake valves and a preventative cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are synchronized for peak volumetric efficiency and throttle response. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
